  "title": "Inside Sales Executive (Ref 25933)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities<br />• Maintaining long-lasting relationships with existing customers through exceptional after-sales service.<br />• Actively sourcing new sales opportunities through cold-calling and emailing.<br />• Developing in-depth knowledge of product features and benefits.<br />• Utilizing virtual meetings to build relationships with new customers.<br />• Processing customers' purchase orders and liaising with the logistics department to ensure the timely delivery of ordered products.<br />• Advising customers on suitable product selection based on their needs and specifications.<br />• Creating a sales pipeline to accurately reflect the relative placement of sales prospects in the purchasing process.<br />• Following up on sales inquiries that are made by potential customers through different channels.<br />• Setting up face-to-face meetings between potential customers and Outside Sales Representatives.<br /><br />Requirements<br />• Minimum diploma / degree in any field with at least 2 years of experience in sales or account management.<br />• Experience in Information Technology would be advantage.<br />• Experience in sales in managed services will be given priority.<br />• Possess excellent communication skills <br />• Excellent negotiation and consultative sales skills.<br />• Effective communication skills.<br />• Exceptional customer service skills.</p><p><br />Licence no: 12C6060</p>",
